<div><p><a href="http://www.springsource.org/dmserver">dm Server</a> 2.0.0.M6 is now available and can be downloaded from <a href="http://www.springsource.com/download/community?project=SpringSource%20dm%20Server&amp;version=2.0.0.M6">here</a>.</p>
